PURPOSE:-
--------
To show the operation of ospfv2 in a four-node network.



SCENARIO:-
---------
In this scenario, there is one CBR session, with node 1 being the source
and node 3 being the destination.  All links are 2Mbps in capacity.

                      3
                    / |
         2Mbps    /   |
                /     |
              /       |
  1 ------- 2         | 2Mbps
     2Mbps    \       |
                \     |
         2Mbps    \   |
                    \ |
                      4

CBR is used to transfer 10 data segments of 512B each at 5 second intervals
starting at 70 minutes into the simulation.



RUN:-
----

Run '<QUALNET_HOME>/bin/qualnet ospfv2-normal-4node.config'.



DESCRIPTION OF THE FILES:-
-------------------------
1. ospfv2-normal-4node.app -  QualNet application configuration file
2. ospfv2-normal-4node.config - the QualNet configuration input file.
3. ospfv2-normal-4node.stat - QualNet statistics collection for CBR and OSPFv2.
4. README - This file.


